# .mailmap — canonical contributor identities for InfraNet Pro.
#
# GitHub builds the repository "Contributors" list from commit history
# (authors + Co-authored-by trailers). This file coalesces auxiliary
# identities onto the single canonical maintainer so the Contributors
# graph shows one author instead of several — without rewriting history.
#
# Format: <canonical name> <canonical email> <email to remap>
muttley1973 <muttley1973@users.noreply.github.com> <noreply@anthropic.com>
